domain.description: A domain name is an identification string that defines a realm of administrative autonomy, authority or control within the Internet.

SEO.description: Search engine optimization (SEO) is the process of improving the quality and quantity of website traffic to a website or a web page from search engines.

DNS.description: The domain name system (DNS) is a naming database in which internet domain names are located and translated into Internet Protocol (IP) addresses.
